{
  "id": "5a093da230f342001231e0b9",
  "title": "良いアイデアなら許可を求めるな",
  "created": 1510555045,
  "updated": 1599722667,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da680c",
      "text": "良いアイデアなら許可を求めるな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da680d",
      "text": "プログラミング言語COBOLを開発した[グレース・ホッパー]の言葉。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1548152323
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad15a98aff09e0000bc0c11",
      "text": "日本では「[許可を求めるな、許しを乞え]」などの言い回しで知られる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523669656,
      "updated": 1534162438
    },
    {
      "id": "5f59d412aff09e0000d62bfa",
      "text": "バリアントがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1599722514,
      "updated": 1599722520
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da680e",
      "text": ">It's easier to ask forgiveness than it is to get permission.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da680f",
      "text": ">Variant: If it's a good idea, go ahead and do it. It is much easier to apologize than it is to get permission.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6810",
      "text": "https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Grace_Hopper",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5f59d41baff09e0000d62bfb",
      "text": "バリアントの方が言葉が補われてて意味が伝わりやすいように思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1599722524,
      "updated": 1599722590
    },
    {
      "id": "5f59d46caff09e0000d62bfe",
      "text": "　「許可を求めるな、許しを乞え」は言葉足らず感",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1599722604,
      "updated": 1599722648
    },
    {
      "id": "5f59d45eaff09e0000d62bfd",
      "text": "　「良いアイデアなら許可を求めずにやれ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1599722590,
      "updated": 1599722667
    },
    {
      "id": "5f59d41baff09e0000d62bfc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1599722524,
      "updated": 1599722524
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6812",
      "text": "\t良いアイデアを思いついたらまずやってみる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1523669613
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6813",
      "text": "  事前に[許可]を求めて待つのはよくない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5a548b6baff09e00006e11c8",
      "text": "  \t成功するのかどうかは事前に分からない、[事後的]にしかわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515490155,
      "updated": 1523669625
    },
    {
      "id": "5a548b58aff09e00006e11c7",
      "text": "  [結果]を見て[修正]する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515490136,
      "updated": 1515490149
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad15a85aff09e0000bc0c10",
      "text": "  \tやってみてダメだったらその時に謝ればよい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523669637,
      "updated": 1523669644
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6815",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1510555045
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6816",
      "text": "[吉岡さん(楽天技術フェロー)による解説 http://d.hatena.ne.jp/hyoshiok/20110205/p1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1523669715
    },
    {
      "id": "5a093da4aff09e0000da6817",
      "text": ">[許可を求めるな。謝罪せよ。]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1510555045,
      "updated": 1534162443
    },
    {
      "id": "5a54923baff09e0000a32924",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515491900,
      "updated": 1515491900
    },
    {
      "id": "5a54923baff09e0000a32923",
      "text": " 同一ネタの別表現 [許可を求めるより謝罪]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515491900,
      "updated": 1515491908
    },
    {
      "id": "5a54923caff09e0000a32925",
      "text": "\t[善は急げ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1515491900,
      "updated": 1546957854
    },
    {
      "id": "5c34b41baff09e00005a4975",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1546957851,
      "updated": 1546957851
    },
    {
      "id": "5c46ede7aff09e0000e46771",
      "text": "\t短い表現",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548152296,
      "updated": 1549203205
    },
    {
      "id": "5c56f704aff09e0000e1f751",
      "text": "\t\t[許可より謝罪]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549203205,
      "updated": 1549203205
    },
    {
      "id": "5c46edeeaff09e0000e46772",
      "text": "\t\t[許可を求めるな]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548152302,
      "updated": 1549203211
    },
    {
      "id": "5c56f707aff09e0000e1f752",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549203208,
      "updated": 1549203208
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee37db8aff09e00004952be",
      "text": "「[謝罪]」という言葉を重たく感じてしまう人も多い。それだと意図に反する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591967161,
      "updated": 1591967254
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee37de9aff09e00004952c0",
      "text": "重要なのは「[許可を求めずにやれ]」の部分。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591967209,
      "updated": 1591967231
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee37dbeaff09e00004952bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591967166,
      "updated": 1591967166
    }
  ]
}